            "type": "text",
            "content": "The stack\n\nA familiar web stack: Next.js for the app, an API layer for business logic, Postgres for truth, Redis for speed, storage for images, queues for work, and sockets for live events.\n\n- Next.js frontend\n- tRPC or REST API\n- PostgreSQL, Prisma, Redis\n- S3/GCS, queues, WebSockets",
