          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "Scaling checklist\n\nBefore adding more services, fix the basics. These are the boring pieces that keep the app fast, safe, and predictable under load.\n\n- Indexes and cursor pagination\n- Redis caching and background queues\n- Object storage plus CDN\n- Rate limits and horizontal APIs\n- Read replicas when reads grow",
            "iconName": "Database",
            "width": null,
            "height": null,
